      <div class="card"><h4>Key Strengths:</h4><ul><li>20+ years historical stock data</li><li>60+ built-in technical indicators</li><li>Fundamental data (earnings, balance sheets)</li><li>Forex and crypto coverage</li></ul></div>
      
